      "id": "PopularPost238125",
      "post_content": "Hah, \"*enchant flying creature*\" love clunky old text on older cards. That aside, there's some pretty stiff competition for other creature hate in {R}, of course there is [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt) but a card more similar to this card would be something like [Flame Sash](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flame Sash)..since they are both cast at sorcery speed and only target creatures. There's better cards out there, with more appropriate art.",
      "posted_by": "tcollins",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost238125\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Hah, \"<i>enchant flying creature</i>\" love clunky old text on older cards. That aside, there's some pretty stiff competition for other creature hate in {R}, of course there is <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a> but a card more similar to this card would be something like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Flame Sash\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flame Sash\">Flame Sash</a>..since they are both cast at sorcery speed and only target creatures. There's better cards out there, with more appropriate art.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '238125'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy44184\">tcollins</span>\r\n                                (4/17/2012 3:11:38 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\"